  "detailed_description": "Cat Jump is a simple platform game. help sissy and her friends through a world full of enemies and dangers or survive in endless mode.<br />\r\nChoose between 4 characters. The game is an indie game developed by a human. Climb up the wall to reach otherwise inaccessible platforms. Use a milk drink to get a 2x boost on coins and buy your life with the coins. Fight with Sissy and her friends against evil enemies such as dogs, zombies and shooting balloons. The game will have many free updates in the future. Its Ideal for Speedrun gamer!",
